1) installation:
  a) Download Git LFS from here [https://git-lfs.github.com/] or
  b) Run this command on your terminal: brew install git-lfs (for macOS)
2) Go to the repository folder and run this command: git lfs install
3) Set the large file format with command: git lfs track "*.so"
4) Push the gitattributes file into the repo: git add .gitattributes

Source: https://git-lfs.github.com/